{"product_id":"noir-core","title":"NOIR CORE","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e JET BLACK WITH EMBROIDERY DETAIL\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e BELT LOOP FOR KEYS OR LIGHTER\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eConstructed from 420 GSM premium cotton fleece for superior structure, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eJet black color with signature Drip Studios embroidery detailing for understated luxury.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSleek ankle zip adds refinement and allows adjustable styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDiscreet belt loop enhances practicality — ideal for holding keys, a lighter, or small essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette designed for relaxed comfort and versatile streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHeavyweight fabric ensures premium feel without compromising flexibility or movement.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePerfect combination of elevated minimalism and streetwear utility for everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article sui